review.description: So I was working and needed some food so I flagged down the first delivery person I saw and asked for a menu. I decided to order the orange chicken with vegetable fried rice. Chicken was good but rice sucked. Very little vegetable's. I also had an order of crab claws for an appetizer which was too much food but good price. 2 claws and I'm good. Orange chicken again not bad and not crispy but sauce was good.
review.author: William C.
